Create Tutor Expertise
POST /api/tutorexpertise
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "TutorID": 1,
  "ModuleID": 101
}

Get All Tutor Expertise
GET /api/tutorexpertise

Get Tutor Expertise by ID
GET /api/tutorexpertise/1/101
(where 1 = TutorID, 101 = ModuleID)

Update Tutor Expertise
PUT /api/tutorexpertise/1/101
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "ModuleID": 102
}

Delete Tutor Expertise
DELETE /api/tutorexpertise/1/101